$ System.Management.Automation.PSMemberInfo (public abstract class)

`System.Management.Automation.PSMemberInfo` is the base class for all
member types with which → Windows/PowerShell implements the → Windows/PowerShell/language/object/Extended-Type-System.

Three important properties of `PSMemberInfo` are:
table { ll
  `Name` ☰ A string that identifies the property with a name.
  `Value` ☰ The actual value of the member that extends an object.
  `TypeNameOfValue` ☰ A string that identifies the → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes[.NET type] of `Value`.
table }

